graph TD
    Start([Turn Resolution Starts]) --> P1[Phase 1: Prepare]
    
    subgraph Phase 1: Prepare
        P1 --> Fetch[Fetch Game, Players, State & Actions]
        Fetch --> Context[Initialize TurnContext]
        Context --> Reset[Reset Visibility & Flags]
    end
    
    Reset --> P2[Phase 2: Intent Resolution]
    
    subgraph Phase 2: Intent Resolution
        P2 --> Loop2[For each Player: Process Actions in Sequence]
        Loop2 --> Validate2[Validate Type: Place/Tether/Anchor]
        Validate2 --> UpdateIdx2[Update Piece & Map Immediately]
    end
    
    UpdateIdx2 --> P3[Phase 3: Combat Resolution]
    
    subgraph Phase 3: Combat Resolution
        P3 --> B_ACT[3a. Resolve Bombardments]
        B_ACT --> V_MOVE[3b. Validate Movement Intents]
        V_MOVE --> I_MOVE[3c. Iterative Non-Conflicting Moves]
        I_MOVE --> BATTLES[3d. Resolve Battles & Collisions]
        BATTLES --> DESTROY[3e. Handle Destruction & Cascading Losses]
        DESTROY --> VICTOR[3f. Apply Victor Movement]
        VICTOR --> F_MOVE[3g. Final Movement Application]
    end
    
    F_MOVE --> P4[Phase 4: Lifecycle & Economy]
    
    subgraph Phase 4: Lifecycle
        P4 --> ELIM[Faction Elimination]
        ELIM --> ACQ[Random Piece Acquisition]
    end
    
    ACQ --> P5[Phase 5: Conclusion]
    
    subgraph Phase 5: Conclusion
        P5 --> WIN[Check Win Conditions]
        WIN --> Save[Save Events & Final State]
        Save --> Transition[Transition Game Status & Turn]
    end
    
    Transition --> End([Turn Resolution Ends])
